root: ^Hello again! Its been a great day with you around.
^Now that the shop is closing up for the day, we could use your help with picking everything up.
^You can just use your MOUSE to drag items into their appropriate bins. For a cafe-master like you, this should practically be child's play!
^Don't forget, RED is for trash, BLUE is for recycle and GREEN is for compost.
^Thanks again for all your hard work! I'll see you again tomorrow.
